item.description: this contains my notes, me logging my thoughts on projects/goals/life etc as i go through them along the way. it would be edited constantly & the latest log would always be on top. 19apr24 late update but lagllama + encoder-decoder model is done. 03apr24 have to complete the time-series-transformers project (also, college’s major project) which includes multivariate data: streamflow, rainfall, temperature etc. i’ve been procrastinating it on forever & my friend did his part of LSTM, i gotta ship something by end of today.
